{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"40":"Prescribed Punishments (Kitab Al-Hudud)"},"section_detail":{"40":{"hadithnumber_first":4351,"hadithnumber_last":4493,"arabicnumber_first":4351,"arabicnumber_last":4493}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4367,"arabicnumber":4367,"text":"حدثنا موسى بن اسماعيل، حدثنا حماد، اخبرنا ثابت، وقتادة، وحميد، عن انس بن مالك، ذكر هذا الحديث قال انس فلقد رايت احدهم يكدم الارض بفيه عطشا حتى ماتوا","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":40,"hadith":17}}]}